都考到就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb59e48aff5690aa4c227f58a6f9c0df478998c7","tid":894450,"uid":119778,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/209a6zOtlL0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F209a6zOtlL0&d=Hc1%2BdZ9%2BT6jd8PNkX1crpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e6fc7c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/209a6zOtlL0</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b23d0d91f077f2e9be76be0151174101e4db2a","tid":894450,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dccf5039dea6645211f295723b8db667644de82","tid":894450,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"「直線七秒」關卡，考生必須在寬30公分、長15公尺的小鐵橋上，維持一定時間的平衡，過程中如果脫離軌道、腳落地，或是太快結束，都算失敗。<br />\n<br />\n好似好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"手放鬆，坐姿唔好夾埋個人，目光放遠，溫柔控制油門，真心易撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我夠膽講，台灣考白牌唔1Take應該驗智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281a72d3f060471ebe2701600f777ae52e296a80","tid":894450,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"每張駕照要花新台幣4萬5千元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港一次沙田20 堂都萬幾蚊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c0f57edef465f6c34f998d01d439e3b6b22ce","tid":894450,"uid":71100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"281a72d3f060471ebe2701600f777ae52e296a80","tid":894450,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:34:12.000Z"