:"一口盐汽水<br />\n1 年前<br />\n你们真严格完善，摩托都需要考试。在大陆，都是买车回来自学的，或者借隔壁邻居的车学开一下。我记得有次我第一次直接开我爸的摩托，车比较高，垫脚尖，刚起步就有个90&deg;湾，离合又控制不好，掉路边水沟了。。。😂😂😂﻿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1baa4ed55519ae47f6eed9db5cb6def7e977e4f","tid":894450,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c77afdd0d3f3ec87c9cbb86584a13247c48a62","tid":894450,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74c1a20918bc4e99cd8166cc08ca2dfced64a530","tid":894450,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"香港都算勁難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦師傅<br />\n英國已經難n倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"英國難喺邊？<br />\n利申英國牌"},{"pid":"04365bcc3827719c786725b80ffb71c068a5e2ec","tid":894450,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1baa4ed55519ae47f6eed9db5cb6def7e977e4f","tid":894450,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c77afdd0d3f3ec87c9cbb86584a13247c48a62","tid":894450,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74c1a20918bc4e99cd8166cc08ca2dfced64a530","tid":894450,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"香港都算勁難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T13:25:34.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦師傅<br />\n英國已經難n倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"英國難喺邊？<br />\n利申英國牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T22:41:05.000Z","msg":"有分catagories已經難好多<br />\n想24歲以下攞a牌好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe4c9a2fd049459f5274453ad3fcf6486426d34","tid":894450,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37c14912baf49ddb9d35600eff3d6c92f4b521a8","tid":